She looked into the bushes.  She realized this bot wasn't going to 
come and she was feeling tired.  "I'm a maximal.  Since I have 
noticed you do not wish to ne known, then I shall not inquire of you 
any longer. Good day to you, who  ever you are." SHe got up, turned, 
and walked over to the other bot who had helped her. "Pray tell me, 
where are you from?  I do not know this area for it is my first time 
out of my own terratory."
She was feleing extremely drained, but none the worse for wear.  "If 
you please tell me, I am hungry, where are the better hunting 
grounds?"
